snippet.title: Forlorn - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Forage, craft, build, hunt, explore. Tackle the wilderness and anything lurking in the shadows in this single-player survival horror adventure.

Forlorn is launching on Steam on May 6th. Wishlist now on https://store.steampowered.com/app/1970440/Forlorn
